Package: housereportstyle
Title: House Style Helpers for Quarto Reports
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Matt",
      family = "Green",
      email = "mgreen@bournemouth.ac.uk",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Author: Matt Green
Maintainer: Matt Green <mgreen@bournemouth.ac.uk>
Description: Reusable Quarto house style, APA-style table, figure,
    scaffold, validation, and scanpath helpers for scientific reports. The
    package supports general report work and retains the foraging-specific
    scanpath workflow from the original reporting helper package.
